/**
 * Noesis Site — i18n Translation System
 * ──────────────────────────────────────
 * Architecture: data-i18n="key" attributes on HTML elements.
 * Default language: English (en).
 * Supported: en, it. Extensible: add new locale to TRANSLATIONS object.
 *
 * Usage:
 *   <span data-i18n="nav.home">Home</span>
 *   <a data-i18n-title="nav.download" href="...">...</a>
 *   <img data-i18n-alt="img.library" ...>
 *   <meta data-i18n-content="meta.description" ...>  (handled via JS)
 *
 * Storage: localStorage key = 'noesis-lang'
 * Toggle: #lang-toggle button in nav
 */

